wbxTreeBundle
=============

a Symfony2 Bundle to handle nested tree structure with Gedmo\NestedTree


Installation
============

Composer
--------

    "require": {
        "wbx/tree-bundle": "*"
    }

    
Add wbxTreeBundle to your application kernel
--------------------------------------------

	// app/AppKernel.php
    public function registerBundles()
    {
        return array(
            // ...
            new wbx\TreeBundle\wbxTreeBundle(),
            // ...
        );
    }

